#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:4 booking/templates/booking/help.html:8
msgid "ヘルプ・よくある質問"
msgstr "Help & FAQ"

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:15
msgid "ご予約について"
msgstr "About Reservations"

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:20
msgid "予約はどのように行いますか？"
msgstr "How do I make a reservation?"

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:24
msgid "トップページの「ご予約」から店舗を選び、ご希望の占い師のカレンダーから空き時間を選択してください。LINE認証後に予約が確定します。"
msgstr ""
"Select a store from \"Reservations\" on the top page, then choose an "
"available time slot from your preferred fortune teller's calendar. Your "
"booking will be confirmed after LINE authentication."

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:30
msgid "予約のキャンセルはできますか？"
msgstr "Can I cancel a reservation?"

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:34
msgid "はい。予約確定後にLINEで届くメッセージ内のリンクからキャンセルが可能です。キャンセル料はかかりません。"
msgstr ""
"Yes. You can cancel via the link in the LINE message you receive after your "
"booking is confirmed. There is no cancellation fee."

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:40
msgid "予約の変更はできますか？"
msgstr "Can I change my reservation?"

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:44
msgid "現在の予約をキャンセルして、改めてご予約ください。"
msgstr "Please cancel your current reservation and make a new one."

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:50
msgid "当日予約はできますか？"
msgstr "Can I make a same-day reservation?"

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:54
msgid "カレンダーに空きがあれば当日でもご予約いただけます。"
msgstr ""
"Yes, same-day reservations are available as long as there are open slots on "
"the calendar."

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:63
msgid "お支払いについて"
msgstr "About Payment"

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:68
msgid "支払い方法は？"
msgstr "What payment methods are available?"

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:72
msgid "オンライン決済（クレジットカード）をご利用いただけます。予約時にLINE経由で決済リンクをお送りします。"
msgstr ""
"Online payment (credit card) is available. A payment link will be sent to "
"you via LINE when you make a reservation."

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:78
msgid "鑑定料金はいくらですか？"
msgstr "How much does a reading cost?"

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:82
msgid "占い師により異なります。各占い師のプロフィールページに料金（1時間あたり）が記載されています。"
msgstr ""
"Prices vary by fortune teller. The rate (per hour) is listed on each fortune"
" teller's profile page."

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:91
msgid "LINE連携について"
msgstr "About LINE Integration"

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:96
msgid "LINEアカウントは必要ですか？"
msgstr "Do I need a LINE account?"

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:100
msgid "はい。ご予約にはLINEログインが必要です。予約通知やタイマー機能もLINEを通じてお届けします。"
msgstr ""
"Yes. LINE login is required to make a reservation. Booking notifications and"
" timer features are also delivered through LINE."

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:106
msgid "LINEの通知はどんな内容ですか？"
msgstr "What kind of notifications will I receive on LINE?"

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:110
msgid "予約確定、キャンセル、鑑定タイマーのリンクなどをお送りします。"
msgstr ""
"You will receive booking confirmations, cancellations, and reading timer "
"links."

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:119
msgid "店舗について"
msgstr "About Our Stores"

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:124
msgid "どの店舗がありますか？"
msgstr "Which stores are available?"

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:128
msgid "現在、新宿・池袋に店舗を展開しています。「店舗情報」メニューから詳細をご確認ください。"
msgstr ""
"We currently have stores in Shinjuku and Ikebukuro. Please check the \"Store"
" Information\" menu for details."

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:134
msgid "営業時間は？"
msgstr "What are the business hours?"

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:138
msgid "各店舗の営業時間は店舗情報ページに記載されています。基本的に9:00〜17:00が鑑定可能時間です。"
msgstr ""
"Business hours for each store are listed on the store information page. "
"Readings are generally available from 9:00 to 17:00."

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:147
msgid "スタッフの方へ"
msgstr "For Staff"

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:152
msgid "マイページにアクセスするには？"
msgstr "How do I access My Page?"

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:156
msgid "管理者から発行されたアカウントでログインし、ナビゲーションの「スタッフページ」からアクセスしてください。"
msgstr ""
"Log in with the account issued by your administrator, then access it from "
"\"Staff Page\" in the navigation menu."

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:162
msgid "シフト（休暇）の設定方法は？"
msgstr "How do I set my schedule (days off)?"

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:166
msgid "マイページ → カレンダー → 日付の「詳細」から、時間単位で休暇を設定できます。「全日休暇にする」で一日全体をブロックすることも可能です。"
msgstr ""
"Go to My Page, then Calendar, then click \"Details\" on the date to set time"
" off by the hour. You can also block an entire day by selecting \"Set as "
"full day off.\""

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:172
msgid "予約の確認方法は？"
msgstr "How do I check reservations?"

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:176
msgid "マイページのカレンダーで「○」が空き、「×」が予約済みです。詳細をクリックすると予約者情報を確認できます。"
msgstr ""
"On the My Page calendar, \"○\" indicates available and \"×\" indicates "
"booked. Click on the details to view the customer's booking information."

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:185
msgid "お問い合わせ"
msgstr "Contact Us"

#: booking/templates/booking/help.html:189
msgid "上記で解決しない場合は、各店舗までお電話いただくか、LINEの公式アカウントよりお問い合わせください。"
msgstr ""
"If the above does not resolve your issue, please call the store directly or "
"contact us through our official LINE account."

